	HardwareInfo.library written by Tomasz "Pony van Deathface" Peczek
	HardwareInfo.library is a libray which will help you with control and
	getting informations abut your hardware.It also have few functions which
	can be use in other purpose.

	This software is subject to the "Standard Amiga FD-Software Copyright Note".
	It is freeware as defined in paragraph 4a.

	For more information please read "AFD-COPYRIGHT" (Version 1.3 or higher).
	If you have any notes or sugestions send it on my address with
	addition "HardwareInfo.library".


				   Tomasz Peczek
				 41-219 Sosnowiec
				 ul.Dlugosza 5/29
				       Poland


